Title: As a user, I want to sign in and sign out so that I can securely access my account.
As a fitness enthusiast, I want to set my fitness goals and upload a profile picture so that my profile is personalized.
As a user, I want to choose from various workout categories and customize my workout plans so that I can follow a routine that suits me.
